                <note rend="inline" type="source">821.6363 Barco/117: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Colombia</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Piles</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Paraphrase]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1928-07-23T12:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 23, 1928—noon</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>39. Department’s telegram No. 38, July 19, 6 p.m. In view of telegram July 20, 6
                    p.m., from Matthews, if it is your feeling that it would be unwise to present
                    the note until you have exchanged views with the Department, you may hold the
                    note and cable your reasons and suggestions for modifying it.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
